lyrics:
[verse]
I'm lost in this maze of emotion
Caught in a whirlwind of devotion
But something holds me back, I can't deny
The fear of love that makes me shy

[chorus]
I love you, oh, I can't pretend
Yet I'm trapped in a love that I can't extend
These words on my lips, they remain unsaid
I love you, but I can't, my heart's filled with dread
